      • onPreExecute

        protected void onPreExecute()
        Called before the Handler loop begins. Registers a timeout, so we do not wait forever for a location. When a timeout occurs, broadcast an Intent containing an error extra, then terminate the thread. Also, requests a location update from the LocationManager.
